0xC6F43D0E.name: ADD_BLIP_FOR_COORD

params.name: x
params.description: The X coordinate to create the blip on.

0xC6F43D0E.description:
Creates a blip for the specified coordinates. You can use `SET_BLIP_` natives to change the blip.

**This is the server-side RPC native equivalent of the client native [ADD_BLIP_FOR_COORD](?\_0x5A039BB0BCA604B6).**
